
  Sandaconda    Ground Type Pokémon

  When it contracts its body, 
  over 220 pounds of sand sprays 
  from its nose.  If it ever runs 
  out of sand, it becomes disheartened. 
  
	Evolution Chain
      Silicobra ► Sandaconda

